# Phase 187: force LF on patch files.
# patch-package requires Unix-style line endings to apply cleanly;
# committing .patch files with CRLF breaks postinstall on clean
# checkouts (even on Windows, because patch-package's underlying
# GNU patch binary expects LF). Narrow scope to *.patch only —
# see ADR-005 context + Kerwyn's guidance on avoiding preemptive
# .gitattributes entries for general *.ts output.
*.patch text eol=lf

# Shell scripts: LF always.
*.sh text eol=lf
